        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Vindicator raid on old server...</P><P>Group had two enchanters (both epic-ed), one rogue (epic), one paladin, one magician (epic), and one druid. </P><P>Both enchanters had dire charmed giant guards. I didn't really notice any loss in exp and we ended up KS-ing every group there, even got final kill on Vindicator.</P><P>Rogue and Paladin probably did enough damage to out weigh the damage done by the two dire charmed giants though.</P><P>Kalyi<BR>Necromancer of Luclin<BR>"Look around you... I am death."</font></td>
